    • addTransaction

      CdrModel addTransaction(String typeCall, Abonent abonent, Instant startTime, Instant endTime)
      Adds a new transaction to the database.
      Parameters:
      typeCall - The type of call (incoming, outgoing).
      abonent - The subscriber making the call.
      startTime - The start time of the call.
      endTime - The end time of the call.
      Returns:
      The CdrModel data model representing the added transaction.
